parsed.explanation: The primary error was a malformed XML tag where the opening angle bracket of the TITLE tag was followed immediately by a double quote (<TITLE"). This was corrected to a proper opening tag (<TITLE>). Additionally, several historical German characters (umlauts and 'ß') were corrupted by unicode sequences (e.g., Gem\u221a\u00baths -> Gemüths; Berichthau\u221a\u00fc -> Berichthauß). These corruptions were normalized to standard German spelling appropriate for the period (ü, ä, ö, ß).
